snippet.title: Sleep Paralysis: The Uncanny Valley Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Demo Available in Spring 2022 here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1941310/Sleep_Paralysis_The_Uncanny_Valley/
Add the game to your wishlist.

Sleep Paralysis: The Uncanny Valley is a story driven first person psychological horror thriller. You will experience a sleep paralysis. You will try to prevent this awful experience. Many of your decisions will affect the story and unfold over the nine different chapters in the game...

Twitter: https://twitter.com/LtdIsightStudio
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/limitedinsightstudios/
Website: https://www.limitedinsight.com
